{"tid":1257380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「比少少士氣大家」5年前 90後學生出來佔中 比市民屌到仆街","createTime":"2019-06-25T13:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T13:24:36.000Z","uid":42246,"like":321,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"03814a4eab1b6ca49227a3159f237abffd682bf6","tid":1257380,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"5年前 90後學生出來佔中 比市民屌到仆街<br />\n搭mtr 書包掛一條黃絲帶 已經可以比廢老屌足成程車<br />\n屌你阻街 阻人搵食 得閒冇野做 搞亂香港<br />\n返到屋企同港豬父母嘈到要分家咁制<br />\n同親戚食飯 成班圍攻你話你搞事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5年後既今日 一樣比人屌<br />\n00後既學生就好似輪迴咁 做緊5年前90後學生做既野<br />\n<br />\n但同時多左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv1EHok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv1EHok.png&h=6cab7493&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1aidu1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1aidu1.png&h=1f172477&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSo83n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSo83n.png&h=7dcea4e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9ju4BK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9ju4BK.png&h=a3fc5351&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOgdMP5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOgdMP5.png&h=fe56552b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5t28AJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5t28AJO.png&h=ddd9b789&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56c4Tvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56c4Tvu.png&h=b0432112&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaRtAJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaRtAJQ.png&h=1cfc777f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f82P4Cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff82P4Cb.png&h=952389e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdHMnoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdHMnoS.png&h=642053fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpMEHoT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpMEHoT.png&h=4a5efbf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYQ6no4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYQ6no4.png&h=b2e975d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXw5CXq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXw5CXq.png&h=baeacc97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6rmbhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6rmbhr.png&h=3ef56ffa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ap2o838.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fap2o838.png&h=828b126b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01ijHo9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01ijHo9.png&h=caaf158a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N44ffKa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN44ffKa.png&h=56f081c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eBjyMQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBjyMQX.png&h=3228a02b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖係集大成 係其他post借）<br />\n<br />\n5年後 起碼依家父母開始理解 社會同政府有問題<br />\n親戚有部分支持學生<br />\n遊行個幾日黑衫成為全港最多人著既顏色<br />\n一車車小巴巴士mtr 都係全黑<br />\n<br />\n依家係同5年前好相似 政府冷處理<br />\n香港人開始善忘 民意因爲影響民生開始轉向<br />\n但同時改變都比5年前多<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時會成功 可能會有下個5年 10後學生上街<br />\n但我信終有一日會成功"},{"pid":"c460bb76aef00f1305ce2d7c8f5ae460ca6be71a","tid":1257380,"uid":42246,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"重有 今次重未完 <br />\n只係開始重複5年前<br />\n5年前<br />\n政府冷處理 &gt; 學生不合作運動（佔中） &gt;影響民意 &gt; 士氣喪失 &gt; 最後清場<br />\n<br />\n但今次重未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff18d95e0d93be90e21bcb425fa7ecfe63ed673","tid":1257380,"uid":256699,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"我相信大多數的人都有良知。加油"},{"pid":"076ff7f205644c2099e870ce5f01545da210bb7e","tid":1257380,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"有冇條片嘅 link？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48db0d090145c38607fc442bd5c5fa5eb3fbf2f9","tid":1257380,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b011c2298f3c0acf652c1aae88c5eac442e8b0","tid":1257380,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076ff7f205644c2099e870ce5f01545da210bb7e","tid":1257380,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"有冇條片嘅 link？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要搵返早幾日tvb"},{"pid":"af91bad8d00623a7c76dbdc53ed85e7d465b9f4e","tid":1257380,"uid":34410,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"連登係今次運動真係團結左好多後生仔<br />\n見到好多學生哥落住雨都派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好洋葱"},{"pid":"a889dedf13717077bb4788c2b377777391c4da8f","tid":1257380,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"各位 聽日見"},{"pid":"bc9f8e9ff5bba8ac8fe73811a75ea9b3dd8b7dff","tid":1257380,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"推！聽日26/6見<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash